Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.29,0:00:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[theme music plays]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.81,0:01:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,SHINIGAMI REALM
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.86,0:01:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[snoring]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.95,0:02:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.74,0:02:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[Deridovely] What?\NA pair of sleeping skulls?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.33,0:02:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hehe, I win again! No
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.37,0:02:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No hard feelings, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.63,0:02:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey there, Ryuk,\Nwould it kill you to join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.84,0:02:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You should come play with us for a change!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.68,0:02:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk] No, I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.81,0:02:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[teacher]\NListen for the voice of God then follow it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.89,0:02:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and know that in time\Nyou will find your salvation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.98,0:02:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[girl 1] I know, I didn't even do\Nanything wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.94,0:02:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,-He just totally snapped at me!\N-[girl 2] Really? So, what did--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.61,0:02:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[teacher] Yagami, are you still with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.57,0:02:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you please translate
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.73,0:02:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,-the following sentence into English?\N-[student] Serious? Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.28,0:02:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.37,0:02:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow the teachings of God\Nand receive his blessings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.28,0:02:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and so, it shall be that the seas\Nwill again become bountiful
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.71,0:02:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and the raging storms will subside.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.29,0:02:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[newscaster 1] Today, at\Napproximately 11:00 a.m. a 32-year-old man
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.17,0:02:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,was found stabbed to death\Nin his apartment
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.46,0:03:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,in the city of Yokohama\NKarigara Prefecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.26,0:03:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Karigara police are treating this case\Nas a homicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.01,0:03:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[newscaster 2] In other news, today,\Nsuspected murderer Naoki Tokuji
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.10,0:03:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,was arrested\Nin the district of Shibuya Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.81,0:03:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He is being held in custody\Nfacing murder charges
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.27,0:03:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,for the brutal slaying\Nof his common-law partner,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.73,0:03:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,who was only 25 at the time of her death.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.61,0:03:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Day in and day out...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.12,0:03:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,the same news on permanent repeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.79,0:03:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk] This is all so... ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.04,0:03:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] This world is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.92,0:03:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk] ...rotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.67,0:03:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,REBIRTH
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.38,0:03:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[teacher] Another noticeable consequence
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.34,0:03:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,is the extinction\Nof many species on the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.30,0:03:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! You--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.64,0:03:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[teacher] Species are now becoming extinct\Nat a faster rate
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.01,0:03:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,than has ever occurred\Nin our recorded history.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.27,0:03:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[student] We already saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.87,0:04:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[indistinct chattering]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.97,0:04:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Death Note?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.51,0:04:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,As in a notebook of death?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.14,0:04:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.52,0:04:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,"How to use it:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.06,0:04:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,the human whose name\Nis written in this notebook…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.15,0:04:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,shall die!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.44,0:04:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.69,0:04:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[smirks]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.82,0:04:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty lame,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.45,0:04:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,not to mention... twisted.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.95,0:04:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really not that different\Nfrom one of those chain letters you get.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.45,0:04:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,A human whose name\Nis written in this notebook shall die?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.66,0:04:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.17,0:04:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[train whistles]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.84,0:05:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,There must be something wrong with me\Nto even consider it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.51,0:05:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,"This note will not take effect
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.97,0:05:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,unless the writer\Nhas the person's face in their mind
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.39,0:05:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,when writing his or her name.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.14,0:05:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, people sharing the same name\Nwill not be affected.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.36,0:05:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If the cause of death is written
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.90,0:05:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,within 40 seconds\Nof writing the person's name,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.40,0:05:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,it will happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.82,0:05:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If the cause of death is not specified,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.95,0:05:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,the person will simply\Ndie of a heart attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.74,0:05:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,After writing the cause of death,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.24,0:05:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,details of the death should be written
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.91,0:05:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,in the next six minutes and 40 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.96,0:05:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.04,0:05:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So, depending on the person\Nyou have in mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.84,0:05:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,you can either kill them easily\Nor painfully. Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.63,0:05:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This is pretty detailed for a prank,\NI'll give them that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.84,0:05:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.93,0:05:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I write a name\Nand that person… dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.85,0:05:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Like anyone would believe that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.70,0:06:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.66,0:06:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.66,0:06:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,on the off chance someone really dies,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.96,0:06:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,would that make me a murderer?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.50,0:06:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah right, it's completely impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.84,0:06:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[newscaster 3] The same assailant\Nwho attacked six people
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.26,0:06:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,at a busy shopping district\Nin Sinjuku yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.30,0:06:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,has struck again,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.26,0:06:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,taking eight people hostage\Nat this daycare center.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.51,0:06:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,His captives include\Nboth children and teachers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.27,0:06:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The police have now identified the suspect
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.14,0:06:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,as 42-year-old Kuro Otoharada,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.48,0:06:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,currently unemployed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.94,0:06:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We expect negotiations\Nto begin immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.57,0:06:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,KUROU OTOHARADA
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.82,0:06:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.19,0:06:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A heart attack in 40 seconds?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.74,0:06:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.53,0:06:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[newscaster 3] At the present time,\Nthat's all the police are telling us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.58,0:06:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[newscaster 4] You can't help
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.79,0:06:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,but feel concerned\Nfor the safety of those hostages.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.00,0:07:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[newscaster 3] You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.29,0:07:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,SHINJUKU PHANTOM KILLER
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.25,0:07:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll continue to monitor\Nthe situation from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.83,0:07:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for that report.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.63,0:07:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you make of this, Mr. Hashimoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.76,0:07:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mr. Hashimoto] Well, one can only hope\Nfor a quick resolution to this situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.14,0:07:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like the notebook doesn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.55,0:07:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh well, I didn't expect it to anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.43,0:07:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[newscaster 4]\NWait, we're seeing something here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.56,0:07:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,There's movement\Nat the front entrance!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.48,0:07:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[newscaster 3]\NThe hostages are coming out,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.40,0:07:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and they all look to be unharmed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.98,0:07:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The Special Forces are taking action;\Nthey're moving in!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.61,0:07:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know\Nif the suspect's been arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.07,0:07:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.15,0:07:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok, we now have confirmation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.11,0:07:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The suspect has been found dead inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.87,0:07:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I repeat, the suspect is now dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.99,0:07:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.00,0:07:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,KUROU OTOHARADA
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.16,0:07:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[newscaster 3] The Special Forces\Nare denying allegations
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.46,0:07:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,that they shot the suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.79,0:07:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[newscaster 4] So, it's quite possible\Nhe was feeling cornered
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.38,0:07:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and decided to commit suicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.63,0:07:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[newscaster 3] Well, according\Nto statements from hostages
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.01,0:07:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,the suspect just suddenly collapsed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.68,0:07:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] A heart attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.26,0:07:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.10,0:08:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coincidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.31,0:08:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This has to be a coincidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.64,0:08:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[Sachiko] Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.90,0:08:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already 6:30, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.94,0:08:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you have cram school tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.19,0:08:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Yeah, I'll be ready in just a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.82,0:08:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Death Note…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.16,0:08:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,it's unlikely,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.28,0:08:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,but if by chance this thing is for real,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.41,0:08:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to test it one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.20,0:08:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,In which case,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.41,0:08:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,it should probably be another criminal.\NBut...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.50,0:08:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,UNIVERSITY ENTRANCE EXAMS
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.54,0:08:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,if he's too well-known,\Nthat will be a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.46,0:08:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If he dies, there's a good possibility
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.71,0:08:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,that news of his death will be covered up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.84,0:08:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to see results right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.26,0:08:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[Sudou] Hey, Ryo buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.26,0:08:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryo] What is it, Sudou?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.51,0:08:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you want to lend me 20 dollars?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.06,0:08:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryo] What, again? But I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.10,0:08:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Light] Sudou.\N-You can't…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.44,0:08:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Maybe I should try killing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.31,0:08:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I should definitely avoid\Nkilling people I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.61,0:08:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Then again,\Ndoes it even really matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.65,0:08:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, would anyone really care
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.36,0:08:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,if I guy like him\Nwas to disappear one day?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.53,0:08:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[student chatter]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.24,0:09:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweet, looks like we'll be hanging
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.66,0:09:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,-at the arcade after school.\N-[smirks]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.91,0:09:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[girl 1] We're having\Na speed dating party tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.17,0:09:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanna come?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.12,0:09:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,-[girl 2] Yeah, of course.\N-Oh yeah, there's no way I'm missing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.92,0:09:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit, why is my mom so useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.30,0:09:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,She's never here to pick me up on time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.09,0:09:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you actually start looking around,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.93,0:09:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,it makes you wonder\Nif you'd be doing society a favor
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.80,0:09:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,by getting rid of all these people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.89,0:09:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[biker] Hey baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.44,0:09:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Where you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.98,0:09:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Come have a little fun with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.81,0:09:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's our Takuo for ya.\NThis guy can spot a hottie a mile away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.94,0:09:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up, little lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.61,0:09:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The name's Takuo Shibuimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.40,0:09:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What do ya say? Come hang out with us,\Npretty lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.24,0:09:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[Lady] Please, I don't want any trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.28,0:09:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[Takuo] You hear that?\NShe doesn't want trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.00,0:09:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that cute? [laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.96,0:09:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[loud heartbeat]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.00,0:09:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.13,0:09:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[Takuo] Let's go, boys.\NStrip her down right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.96,0:09:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.55,0:09:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Takuo laughs]\N-[Lady] No! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.17,0:09:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.26,0:09:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[screams] Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.14,0:10:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[thugs whooping]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.35,0:10:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,TAKUO SHIBUIMARU\NACCIDENTAL DEATH
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.13,0:10:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Now, what will happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.31,0:10:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[Takuo] Hey, wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.02,0:10:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Takuo, look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.65,0:10:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.28,0:10:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light gasps] That settles it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.78,0:10:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The Death Note...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.49,0:10:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's for real!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.91,0:10:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[thug 1] Oh man!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.08,0:10:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-Takuo!\N-[thug 2] Stupid kid,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.87,0:10:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,he just came outta nowhere! [screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.38,0:10:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk] Now then,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.88,0:10:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd better get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.61,0:10:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk] It's been five days.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.32,0:11:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.74,0:11:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd better get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.62,0:11:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? You headed somewhere, Ryuk?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.29,0:11:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hate to tell you, but our whole world\Nlooks like this. [chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.62,0:11:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true, but I've dropped\Nmy Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.42,0:11:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughter]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.00,0:11:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You really messed things up, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.30,0:11:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.51,0:11:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you already trick the Old Man\Nto get a second book?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.51,0:11:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you dropped both of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.43,0:11:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You must have some idea\Nwhere you dropped the thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.93,0:11:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk] Yeah, the human world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.14,0:11:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[Deridovely and Gook] What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.25,0:11:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[Sachiko] What a nice surprise!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.71,0:12:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't expecting you home so early.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.59,0:12:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.59,0:12:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi mom. It's because…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.51,0:12:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.06,0:12:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.14,0:12:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,the results of the nationwide exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.39,0:12:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.52,0:12:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.23,0:12:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodness! Number one, again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.44,0:12:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the highest scores you've had.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.44,0:12:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Yeah, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.69,0:12:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to study in my room,\Nso please don't interrupt me, ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.40,0:12:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,As you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.91,0:12:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh Light,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.37,0:12:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,do you want anything at all, dear?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.12,0:12:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You can ask for whatever you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.74,0:12:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm fine, Mom. Thanks though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.96,0:12:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already got what I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.05,0:12:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles quietly]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.80,0:12:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughs maniacally]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.98,0:12:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk] You've taken quite a liking to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.36,0:13:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.57,0:13:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No reason to act surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.20,0:13:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the Shinigami, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.20,0:13:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That used to be my notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.62,0:13:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Judging by your laughter,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.12,0:13:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,you've already figured out
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.37,0:13:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,that what you have\Nis no ordinary notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.59,0:13:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Shinigami,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.26,0:13:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,a God of Death, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.93,0:13:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm not surprised. In fact…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.31,0:13:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuk...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.89,0:13:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting... for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.85,0:13:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.73,0:13:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] I've already figured out that\Nthis Death Note that I've found is real.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.90,0:13:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It didn't take me long.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.57,0:13:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And now that I've witnessed\Nthe proof of its power,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.28,0:13:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I only feel more confident\Nwhat I'm gonna do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.58,0:13:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.37,0:13:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I certainly wasn't expecting this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.29,0:13:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Several Death Notes have made their way\Ninto the human world in the past,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.62,0:14:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,but you're the first\Nto have written this many names.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.84,0:14:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at how many people\Nyou’ve killed in only five days.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.42,0:14:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Most are reluctant to write this much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.76,0:14:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already prepared myself, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.93,0:14:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I used the notebook even though\NI knew it belonged to a Shinigami,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.18,0:14:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and now that Shinigami has come.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.68,0:14:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what will happen to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.48,0:14:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're here to take my soul, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.48,0:14:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, what do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.69,0:14:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that some fantasy\Nyou humans came up with?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.36,0:14:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna do anything to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.91,0:14:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The notebook becomes\Npart of the human realm
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.37,0:14:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,from the very moment it touches the earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.79,0:14:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, the notebook is now yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.50,0:14:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] This… is mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.46,0:14:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't want it,\Njust give it to someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.25,0:14:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you give it away,\NI'd have no choice
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.42,0:14:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,but to erase your memories\Nof the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.80,0:14:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So, then, you're saying
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.09,0:14:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I can use the Death Note all I want\Nand I won't be punished?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.26,0:14:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just say this,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.35,0:14:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,you will feel the fear and pain
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.27,0:14:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,known only to humans\Nwho have used the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.19,0:15:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And when it's your time to die,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.36,0:15:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,it will fall on me to write your name\Nin my Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.19,0:15:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Be warned,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.36,0:15:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,any human who's used a Death Note
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.41,0:15:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,can neither go to heaven nor hell\Nfor eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.08,0:15:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.12,0:15:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.29,0:15:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you have something\Nto look forward to after you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.76,0:15:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,-[gasps]\N-[Sachiko] Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.76,0:15:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.18,0:15:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.93,0:15:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.93,0:15:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you'd like some apples.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.43,0:15:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The neighbors brought them over for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.68,0:15:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Why on earth is it so dark in your room?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.23,0:15:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-You'll ruin your eyesight!\N-[Light] What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.23,0:15:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom can't see him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.82,0:15:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk] That notebook you found\Noriginally belonged to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.70,0:15:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and since you're now using it,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.41,0:15:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,you are the only one able to see me,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.83,0:15:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and of course, my voice
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.41,0:16:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,can only be heard by you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.25,0:16:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.37,0:16:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,the Death Note is the bond\Nbetween Light, the human
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.21,0:16:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and Ryuk, the Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.88,0:16:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Mhmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.84,0:16:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yum.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.01,0:16:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I just have one more question\NI wanna ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.09,0:16:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Ryuk chomping]\N-Why was I chosen for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.76,0:16:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you even listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.85,0:16:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[swallows]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.73,0:16:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Apples in the human world\Nare worth the trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.27,0:16:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the best way to describe these?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.52,0:16:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Juicy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.82,0:16:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Just answer my question?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.69,0:16:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[scoffs] I didn't choose you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.82,0:16:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you see?\NThis is all just an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.53,0:16:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You actually thought you were chosen\Nbecause you're so smart or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.16,0:16:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so vain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.95,0:16:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It just happened to fall around here,\Nand you just happened to pick it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.83,0:16:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's all there is to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.54,0:16:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I wrote the instructions\Nin English,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.84,0:16:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,the most popular language\Nin the human world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.21,0:16:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why did you drop it\Nin the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.55,0:16:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You even wrote down specific instructions,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.72,0:16:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,so don't try telling me\Nthis was an accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.43,0:16:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You're asking me why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.81,0:17:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it 'cause I was bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.98,0:17:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You were bored?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.98,0:17:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk] The truth is Shinigami haven't got\Nmuch to do these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.36,0:17:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Most of the time we're either taking naps\Nor gambling.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.78,0:17:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If you take the time to write names\Nin your Death Note,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.28,0:17:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,the others just laugh at you\Nfor working so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.45,0:17:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you wrote the name\Nof another Shinigami,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.74,0:17:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,it'd be pointless\Nbecause they wouldn't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.91,0:17:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And since we live in the Shinigami Realm,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.16,0:17:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,it brings us no amusement to kill those\Nin the human world either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.92,0:17:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I figured I'd have more fun\Nif I came down here myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.63,0:17:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I'm surprised at how many names\Nyou've written,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.97,0:17:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,but I wanna know why you only wrote
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.89,0:17:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,the cause of death for that guy\Nwho was hit by the truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.68,0:17:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't write down\Nthe cause of death,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.60,0:17:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,the victim dies of a heart attack,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.44,0:17:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's probably the best thing\Nabout the Death Note, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.94,0:17:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.15,0:17:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, I've already exhausted\Nthe list of the world's major criminals,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.99,0:17:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and eventually,\NI'm going to get rid of them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.66,0:18:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the point of doing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.87,0:18:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only a matter of time\Nbefore people figure out
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.95,0:18:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,that these criminals\Nare being eliminated by someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.96,0:18:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I want the world to know of my existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.17,0:18:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That there's someone out there\Npassing righteous judgement on the wicked!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.34,0:18:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Why even bother?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.88,0:18:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to achieve\Nby passing judgement on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.01,0:18:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, why do you care?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.55,0:18:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Because…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.93,0:18:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been bored too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.73,0:18:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't ready to believe it at first,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.85,0:18:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's obvious now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.27,0:18:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something\Nabout the Death Note itself
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.15,0:18:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,that makes humans want to try it out\Nat least once.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.95,0:18:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I killed them both.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.82,0:18:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I really… I killed two men.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.12,0:18:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Those were human lives,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.08,0:18:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,it won't be overlooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.91,0:18:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.21,0:18:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,who am I to pass judgement on others?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.92,0:18:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.05,0:18:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'm wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.80,0:18:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This is exactly\Nwhat I've been thinking about lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.97,0:19:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This world is rotting,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.55,0:19:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and those who are making it rot\Ndeserve to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.93,0:19:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone has to do it, so why not me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.27,0:19:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it means sacrificing\Nmy own mind and soul,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.14,0:19:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,it's worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.31,0:19:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.94,0:19:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,can't go on like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.19,0:19:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I've wondered…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.69,0:19:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,what if someone else\Npicked up this notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.03,0:19:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anyone out there, other than me,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.91,0:19:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,who would be willing\Nto eliminate the vermin from the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.78,0:19:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't do it,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.33,0:19:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,then who will?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.58,0:19:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just it; there's no one,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.04,0:19:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,but I can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.96,0:19:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.17,0:19:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the only one who can.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.13,0:19:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.50,0:19:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,using the Death Note,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.92,0:19:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll change the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.72,0:19:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.81,0:19:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.07,0:20:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.79,0:20:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.25,0:20:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] At first, I wrote the names\Nof the worst criminals I could think of.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.30,0:20:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I was cleaning up the world,\None name at a time,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.38,0:20:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,so that eventually no one will ever\Ndo anything evil again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.64,0:20:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And while the truly guilty ones who\Ndeserve to be punished for their crimes
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.73,0:20:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,die of heart attacks,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.10,0:20:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,the people who are less guilty\Nbut who still make trouble for others
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.19,0:20:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,will slowly be erased\Nthrough disease and accidental death.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.82,0:20:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, and only then,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.28,0:20:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,the world will start moving\Nin the right direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.20,0:20:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be a new world, free of injustice,\Nand populated by people
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.66,0:20:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,who I've judged to be honest,\Nkind, and hardworking.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.04,0:20:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you did that, it would make you\Nthe only bad person left.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.12,0:20:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I have no idea\Nwhat you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.67,0:20:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a hard-working honor student
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.59,0:21:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,who is considered to be one of Japan's\Nbest and brightest.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.30,0:21:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And I…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.14,0:21:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I will become the God of this New World.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.81,0:21:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just as I thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.39,0:21:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,humans are so interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.86,0:21:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,TO BE CONTINUED
